OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: How much
OL,4,Ccompensation will victims receive?
OL,6,FThe documents say that those living
OL,7,Fwith HIV or at least two severe
OL,8,Fillnesses could be entitled to at
OL,9,Fleast #2 million per person.
OL,11,FThere is no limit to how much a person
OL,12,Fcould receive. The government states
OL,13,Fthe figures shared below are not final
OL,14,Fnumbers and should be treated with
OL,15,Fcaution.
