OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: How much
OL,4,Ccompensation will victims receive?
OL,6,FThe 'injury award' recognises the
OL,7,Fphysical and mental injury and
OL,8,Femotional distress caused or will be
OL,9,Fcaused, while another award calculates
OL,10,Fthe 'financial loss' suffered by
OL,11,Fvictims and their families.
OL,13,FA 'social impact' award will look at
OL,14,Fthe societal prejudice or social
OL,15,Fisolation a person may have suffered
OL,16,Fdue to the viruses they contracted,
OL,17,Fwith many victims saying they've been
OL,18,Fforced to conceal their illnesses as a
OL,19,Fresult of the stigma associated with
OL,20,FHIV and Hepatitis.
