OL,6,FThe 'care award' will assess the past
OL,7,Fand future care needs and associated
OL,8,Fcosts for victims, while the 'autonomy
OL,9,Faward' recognises additional redress
OL,10,Ffor the distress caused by the impact
OL,11,Fof the disease, including interference
OL,12,Fwith family and private life - for
OL,13,Fexample, the loss of opportunity to
OL,14,Fhave children.
